  "body": "### Component\r\n\r\nForge\r\n\r\n### Describe the feature you would like\r\n\r\nSupport for the `ETH_PASSWORD` env var and `--password-file` flag was added to cast in https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/pull/3632 .\r\n\r\nCan this be added for forge wallet controls as well? I'd like to use this with deploys and such.\r\n\r\n### Additional context\r\n\r\nIt's possible this is a bug too. I'm running the following command with `ETH_PASSWORD` set (cast works properly):\r\n\r\n`forge script script/Deploy.s.sol:Deploy --use solc:0.8.10 --rpc-url $ETH_RPC_URL --sender $ETH_FROM --broadcast`",
